日)","rule_no":"第九條","content":"　　本條例自公布日施行。","relates":{}}],"law_reasons":{"第三條":"　　增列第二項。並規定三等親內之舉發人不得領取該獎金。另對於查緝獎金之條文應全數刪除。","第四條":"　　酌作文字修正，並刪除後段文字。"},"law_history":[{"進度":"一讀","會議日期":"920605","立法紀錄":"92卷34期3308號一冊 2-2頁","立法紀錄連結":"https:\/\/lis.ly.gov.tw\/ttscgi\/lgimg?@xdd!cecac8c8c9c8cfc7caca81c6cdcccbcfcec4cfcfcfcdc4cfcfcfcd","主提案":"朱星羽","關係文書":[["提案","https:\/\/lis.ly.gov.tw\/lgcgi\/lgmeetimage?cfcacfcccecacfcec5cccbc7d2cccacc"]]},{"進度":"一讀","會議日期":"930102","立法紀錄":"93卷4期3338號上冊 5-5頁","立法紀錄連結":"https:\/\/lis.ly.gov.tw\/ttscgi\/lgimg?@xdd!cecac8c8c9c8cfc7caca81c6cccfcbcfcec4cfcfcfcac4cfcfcfca","主提案":"廖本煙","關係文書":[["提案","https:\/\/lis.ly.gov.tw\/lgcgi\/lgmeetimage?cfcacfcbcec9cfcec5c9cac8d2c9cac6"]]},{"進度":"委員會審查","會議日期":"921023","立法紀錄":"92卷48期3322號下冊 195-218頁","立法紀錄連結":"https:\/\/lis.ly.gov.tw\/ttscgi\/lgimg?@xdd!cecac8c8c9c8cfc7caca81c6cdcbc7cfccc4cfcec6cac4cfcdcec7","關係文書":[]},{"進度":"二讀(廣泛討論)","會議日期":"921204","立法紀錄":"92卷57期3331號一冊 36-42頁","立法紀錄連結":"https:\/\/lis.ly.gov.tw\/ttscgi\/lgimg?@xdd!cecac8c8c9c8cfc7caca81c6cdcac8cfcec4cfcfccc9c4cfcfcbcd","關係文書":[["審查報告","https:\/\/lis.ly.gov.tw\/lgcgi\/lgmeetimage?cfcacfcacfc7cfccc5ccd2ca"]]},{"進度":"二讀(逐條討論)","會議日期":"930402","立法紀錄":"93卷19期3353號上冊 28-31頁","立法紀錄連結":"https:\/\/lis.ly.gov.tw\/ttscgi\/lgimg?@xdd!cecac8c8c9c8cfc7caca81c6cccec6cfcec4cfcfcdc7c4cfcfccce","關係文書":[]},{"進度":"二讀(逐條討論)","會議日期":"940409","立法紀錄":"93卷20期3354號上冊 27-36頁","立法紀錄連結":"https:\/\/lis.ly.gov.tw\/ttscgi\/lgimg?@xdd!cecac8c8c9c8cfc7caca81c6cccdcfcfcec4cfcfcdc8c4cfcfccc9","關係文書":[]},{"進度":"三讀","會議日期":"940409","立法紀錄":"93卷20期3354號上冊 36-36頁","立法紀錄連結":"https:\/\/lis.ly.gov.tw\/ttscgi\/lgimg?@xdd!cecac8c8c9c8cfc7caca81c6cccdcfcfcec4cfcfccc9c4cfcfccc9","關係文書":[]}],"commit_at":"20040421"}]